---
title: `$union::__()`
description: Create comment markup.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
Union::__($content, $dent = 0, $block = N);
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
$test_1 = Union::__('test comment');
$test_2 = Union::__('test comment', 1);
$test_3 = Union::__('test comment', 0, ' ');
$test_4 = Union::__('test comment', 1, ' ');
~~~

Result:

~~~ .php
$test_1 = '<!--
test comment
-->';
~~~

~~~ .php
$test_2 = '  <!--
test comment
  -->';
~~~

~~~ .php
$test_3 = '<!-- test comment -->';
~~~

~~~ .php
$test_4 = '  <!-- test comment -->';
~~~